  m_Script: {fileID: 11500000, guid: 6afaf71966ea65643a2583b7ff0771a3, type: 3}
  m_Name: Albedo_Dialogue_Quest0
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: Assembly-CSharp::DialogueData
  npcName: Albedo
  dialogueLines:
  - "Xiao... you\u2019ve finally opened your eyes."
  - Take it easy. You've survived a nightmare, but the waking world is no kinder.
  - I carry a heavy burden... Your comrades fought bravely, but they didn't make
    it.
  - We laid them to rest on the quiet hill at the far end of the village.
  - The Shadow Entity has stolen the Heartstone. The encroaching darkness is already
    taking root.
  - Go to the hill. Pay your final respects. When you are ready, return to me...
    we have much to discuss.
